Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.71,0:00:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,诶 死过去了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.72,0:00:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不会吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.01,0:00:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你好…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.28,0:00:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你这人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.22,0:00:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,还蛮可爱的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.45,0:00:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,兔子？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.65,0:01:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,店长 刚才里面有人…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.95,0:01:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.49,0:01:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.84,0:01:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.30,0:01:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,商店街的庙会？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.89,0:01:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,音乐表演会？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.54,0:02:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 会议正式开始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.36,0:02:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎各位出席商店街青年部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.35,0:02:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,庙会活动委员临时集会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.45,0:03:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我是今天的主席
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,羽泽咖啡厅的羽泽鸫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.85,0:03:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来开始点名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.41,0:03:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,山吹面包房的沙绫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.25,0:03:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,北泽肉铺的育美
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.74,0:03:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好次～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.06,0:03:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,青年部太鼓带头人巴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.04,0:03:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,和她的妹妹亚子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.61,0:03:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,再为吾呈上暗黑的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.84,0:03:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,甘甜又气泡充足的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.51,0:03:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,再来一杯可乐是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.48,0:03:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.02,0:03:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,话说你怎么在这儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.34,0:03:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,有商店街之处必有我摩卡！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.65,0:03:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,她是山吹面包房的常客了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.89,0:03:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,今天我们还迎来了一位新成员
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.86,0:03:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,旭汤的朝日六花
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.12,0:03:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,今天我作为Galaxy的工作人员跟各位见面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.03,0:03:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,请大家多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.95,0:03:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我是受店长委托
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,可是还不是很清楚状况
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.62,0:03:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.25,0:03:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我们几个也在慢慢摸索着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.42,0:04:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,其实吧 是这次商店街要搞个活动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.75,0:04:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我看到海报了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,「身心健康 Go Go」庙会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.58,0:04:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,健康Go！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,之前我被商店街的老一辈们点了名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.64,0:04:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我们想招呼一批年轻人进来保持商店街的活力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.11,0:04:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.46,0:04:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,小鸫 来弄一个Love啥的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.86,0:04:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,就那个Love
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Love？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是和巴一起弄了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.32,0:04:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,乐器的演奏会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你说演唱会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(991,975)}Live
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.14,0:04:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,真怀念咱的青春时代啊 小米
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.82,0:04:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,咱几个也穿校服整了一场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.98,0:04:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,三味线的演奏会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.26,0:04:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,高中生最棒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.19,0:04:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好青春呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.75,0:04:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,真好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.55,0:04:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,然后Afterglow就决定要出演了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.73,0:04:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,听说商店街的各个店铺都会帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.58,0:04:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.10,0:04:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello-Happy你们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.07,0:05:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要弄可乐饼Live哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.36,0:05:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,可乐饼Live？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,PoPiPa的各位不出场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.45,0:05:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 想法不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.55,0:05:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,大家一起来肯定更开心的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.51,0:05:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你能不能去问一声呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,嘛 虽然已经能猜到回答了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,去！当然想去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我就知道你会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.85,0:05:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们主办的演唱会那边没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.23,0:05:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,现在正在列场地的清单呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.44,0:05:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那可是我做的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.73,0:05:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那个庙会是每年都办的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.01,0:05:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我们家会摆摊卖面包
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,还有育美家的可乐饼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.56,0:05:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那个可好吃了 含税才86日元
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.52,0:05:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那会场呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.56,0:05:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他们说会在户外现搭一个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.48,0:05:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,露天演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.33,0:05:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,真好啊 露天演唱会…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,说了两遍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.77,0:05:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟很重要嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.80,0:05:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,露天演唱会…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.00,0:05:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,第三遍！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,相当重要哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.16,0:05:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就回复她们说要参加哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.45,0:05:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,要和Afterglow一起演出吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.79,0:05:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,还得决定曲目呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.50,0:06:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,得开始练习了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.17,0:06:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,大家一起来拼命练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.10,0:06:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,巴 节奏太赶了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.22,0:06:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我太期待健康Go啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.73,0:06:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,巴你最喜欢庙会了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.37,0:06:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,太鼓那边要怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,还用说吗 当然也全力以赴了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.47,0:06:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,加油哦 小巴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.69,0:06:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,再不快点山吹面包房就要关门了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.06,0:06:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然要面对吃不上面包的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.78,0:06:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我找不到活下去的意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.31,0:06:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那就快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.26,0:06:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好次～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,听说是在这里搭建舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.83,0:06:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,商店街的老一辈现在也很期待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.61,0:06:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 她们好像还做了团扇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.72,0:06:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,燃起来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.70,0:06:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.04,0:06:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.56,0:07:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,各位 加油吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,预备 一 二 哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为巴你也会配合的 好过分！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.72,0:07:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这部分就照往常来就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.52,0:07:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,绯玛丽好来劲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,休息
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.38,0:07:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,给各位奖励
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.34,0:07:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,预备
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.85,0:07:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,这个！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,果然还是巧克力螺好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.79,0:07:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟这是山吹面包房的所在地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.93,0:07:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,干脆把店名加进歌词里弄成广告一样？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,想买面包哪里去？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.44,0:07:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,就去山吹面包房～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.09,0:07:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不买呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.45,0:07:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,难得一场庙会 还是想尽兴一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.61,0:07:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要唱Happy Happy Party？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.51,0:07:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定嗨得起来！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.75,0:08:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,曲目编排就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.60,0:08:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 还不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.70,0:08:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思我迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.33,0:08:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Galaxy已经同意给我们租器材了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.56,0:08:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们提前一天去搬出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.29,0:08:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,还有 什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.22,0:08:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好来劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.74,0:08:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.50,0:08:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,因为又要准备庙会 又想多练习一些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,要是太努力又累倒了可不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.32,0:08:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是哦 那我会尽量不累倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.79,0:08:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,又来劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.08,0:08:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,还是一如既往啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.71,0:08:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你们啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.37,0:08:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,夕阳好美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.51,0:08:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.02,0:08:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在初中的学园祭表演之后看到的夕阳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.21,0:08:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么可能忘记呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那毕竟是我们的第一场演出啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.64,0:09:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,在那之后也看了好多次夕阳呢 我们五个人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.98,0:09:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 这不是LOCK吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,LOCK！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.26,0:09:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.28,0:09:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Poppin'Party也决定参演
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.61,0:09:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,快给我拿下来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.55,0:09:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,特意为我们贴的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.64,0:09:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 LOCK！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.30,0:09:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.61,0:09:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是咱们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.39,0:09:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 那是之前的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Poppin'Party 即将开演！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.49,0:10:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这可是LOCK特意帮我们做的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.25,0:10:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,还想在这边唱歌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.49,0:10:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.09,0:10:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是最后一件了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那就搬去舞台吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.10,0:10:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 蔬菜店会用车帮我们运过去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.01,0:10:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,弄完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.15,0:10:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,真期待明天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.98,0:10:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,大家要玩得尽兴哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.31,0:10:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.57,0:10:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢大家风雨兼程
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.15,0:10:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我宣布 第19届身心健康 Go Go庙会 正式开始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,请看可乐饼Live
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.96,0:10:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我买二十个！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.69,0:10:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,因为庙会名字有Go
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.74,0:10:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,所以五百日元Go Go！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.69,0:10:55.52,Tips,,0,0,0,,注：日语“五”与英文Go发音相近
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.68,0:10:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Go Go！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.06,0:10:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是Afterglow
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.08,0:11:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,第一首曲子是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然下起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.63,0:11:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,下雨吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不好 那些设备！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.13,0:11:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,只能再把它们搬回Galaxy了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.78,0:11:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我去帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.32,0:11:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我去叫好卡车
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.92,0:11:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,原定在庙会广场进行的演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.74,0:11:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,因下雨暂时中止
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.51,0:11:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,再重复一遍…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.38,0:11:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不介意的话就用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.84,0:11:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 是羽泽咖啡厅的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.30,0:11:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这雨会停吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.81,0:11:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,天气预报虽然说到了傍晚就会停
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.12,0:11:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,鞋子都湿透了 兴致全被浇没了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.90,0:11:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我好想演出啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.72,0:11:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,要吃点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:11:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这是亚子送的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:12:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 我也有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.29,0:12:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,大家也把它分了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.61,0:12:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 山吹面包房
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.45,0:12:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我开吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.55,0:12:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.62,0:12:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,巧克力螺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,难道你们已经习惯露天演唱会了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.39,0:12:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,诶 没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.53,0:12:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我看你们都那么冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.23,0:12:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,现在也只能等着啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不管发生什么 都只是照常发挥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.64,0:12:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Afterglow是怎么聚在一起的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.12,0:12:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就是回过神来就在一起了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟都是一起长大的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.97,0:12:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,小学还在同一个班呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.86,0:12:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但是初二的时候 只有兰被分到了别的班
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.93,0:12:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,然后五个人就难得见一面了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.95,0:12:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,乐队…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,来组乐队吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 鸫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:12:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我想过怎么让我们五个人又能在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.20,0:13:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,所以觉得大家一起办一件事的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.41,0:13:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,一定会有很多时间聚起来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.51,0:13:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我觉得可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.76,0:13:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好像好久没看到兰的这种表情了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.80,0:13:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,想到什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.86,0:13:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.37,0:13:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Omnis 意思是一切
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.68,0:13:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然听着很帅 但总感觉不对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.14,0:13:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ultra Violet
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.90,0:13:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.91,0:13:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,紫外线
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.06,0:13:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,还是取个有意义的名字比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.33,0:13:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,确实是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.64,0:13:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟乐队叫紫外线的 还是太难懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.96,0:13:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,要有我们风格的名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.92,0:13:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,夕阳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.41,0:13:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我们总是在放学之后练习
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.47,0:13:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不就是傍晚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,确实是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,翻译成英语的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:13:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunset？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:13:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(929,975)}日落
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.25,0:13:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Evening？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.25,0:13:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(929,975)}夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.53,0:14:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Afterglow
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这个名字觉得如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.23,0:14:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.16,0:14:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,决定了 我们的乐队名字就叫Afterglow
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.38,0:14:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你们一直都在一起的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,简单说来就是难舍难分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.28,0:14:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟都经历过那么多事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.16,0:14:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,有的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.46,0:14:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,有的有的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.90,0:14:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 咱还有个大目标对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,诶 那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.39,0:14:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,什么什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.79,0:14:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,朝着武道馆前进！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,武道馆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.40,0:14:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,就像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还是像平常一样在一起才最开心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.24,0:14:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.95,0:14:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,感受到了各位深厚的友情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.33,0:14:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,太夸张啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.28,0:15:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,雨小了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.62,0:15:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,几乎停了 能不能再开演呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.63,0:15:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,现在开始准备的话 应该能赶得上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.45,0:15:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,但是舞台就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.64,0:15:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,还有拖把吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.26,0:15:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 放在商店街的仓库里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.63,0:15:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们去搬器材吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.65,0:15:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,但是不能再用车了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.07,0:15:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.23,0:15:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,诶～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.74,0:15:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不行的啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好重
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.93,0:15:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,先放下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,交给我来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.28,0:15:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,LOCK？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.59,0:15:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,LOCK 这样太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.38,0:15:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,LOCK…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.65,0:15:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,还是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.31,0:15:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,都叫你别太勉强了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.68,0:15:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(610,1055)}看招！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.31,0:15:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1000,1055)}巴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.64,0:15:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.46,0:15:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.11,0:15:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,能搬上去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.56,0:16:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你们要开演唱会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.11,0:16:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.35,0:16:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来 要在舞台上开Love…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.98,0:16:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,米婆婆 是Live
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.88,0:16:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,哦？要开演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.04,0:16:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都来看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.22,0:16:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,友希那
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.96,0:16:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那服装怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.42,0:16:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这都湿透了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.08,0:16:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.96,0:16:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们上场了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.20,0:16:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是校服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.68,0:16:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,麻烦各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.13,0:16:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,放晴了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.23,0:16:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,说不定是护身符的功效呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.19,0:16:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我也有带一个哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.37,0:16:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我也有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.35,0:16:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,都有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.15,0:16:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那就照常发挥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.61,0:16:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,燃起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.67,0:16:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:16:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,各位 尽情上吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.72,0:17:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,预备 一 二 哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.02,0:17:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 气氛都这么好了 还不配合我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这也跟平时一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.55,0:17:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.89,0:18:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.35,0:18:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,她们五个人都照常发挥多少次了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.70,0:19:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢大家！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.46,0:19:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,PoPiPa
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.16,0:19:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,该你们上场了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.87,0:19:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.71,0:19:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,LOCK 我们出发了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.96,0:19:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.11,0:19:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你LOCK
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.44,0:20:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.28,0:20:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一件事请让我们同大家分享
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.41,0:20:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的主办演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.84,0:20:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,将在本商店街的Live House Galaxy里举办
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎来看！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.36,0:20:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我没听说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.00,0:20:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,咱又没说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.46,0:20:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我们想给你个惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,实在太惊喜了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.80,0:20:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.75,0:20:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是北极星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.86,0:21:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah！姐姐超帅的！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.79,0:21:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,有感觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.34,0:22:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,朝着武道馆前进吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.71,0:22:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,有共同的目标也挺好的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.04,0:22:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也要一点点进步
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.46,0:22:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.81,0:22:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,首先是在Galaxy的主办演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.82,0:23:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.46,0:23:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,来 茄子～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.15,0:23:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.10,0:23:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,里美 拍到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.35,0:23:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,再靠近一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.53,0:23:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,来这边嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.55,0:23:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,有咲你不靠近一点拍不到的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.15,0:23:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,里美也过来！
